|title = Asthma and sex
|journal = Indian J Chest Dis Allied Sci
|year = 2001
|pages = 135-137
|volume = 43
|publisher = medind.nic.in
|url = http://medind.nic.in/iae/t01/i3/iaet01i3p135.pdf?origin=publicationDetail
|access-date = 2015-05-23
|archive-date = 2020-06-16
|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200616203906/http://medind.nic.in/iae/t01/i3/iaet01i3p135.pdf?origin=publicationDetail
}}</ref>

==可能因素列表==
* 对精子或精液的过敏反应
* 对神经递质或类似物质的[[过敏|过敏反应]]
* 射精管梗阻
* 突发和长期的[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]的再摄取
* {{le|麸质敏感性|Gluten sensitivity}}
* [[營養不良|營養不良]]或维生素缺乏
* 铜、汞、铅、面粉、硅或其他物质[[毒物|中毒]]
* 创伤/[[創傷後心理壓力緊張症候群|PTSD]]相关联的心身反应压垮神经系统
* 病毒、细菌或寄生虫[[感染|感染]]
* [[精子|精子]]的持续泄漏造成疲劳
* [[甲状腺功能亢进症|甲状腺功能亢进症]]
* [[腎上腺|腎上腺]]功能障碍
* 缺乏[[孕酮|孕酮]]
* [[性成瘾|性成瘾]]
* [[色情成瘾|色情成瘾]]
* [[情绪抑郁|情绪抑郁]]
* [[家族性植物神经失调综合征|家族性自主神經失調綜合症]]、{{le|端坐性心搏過速症|Postural orthostatic tachycardia syndrome|端坐性心搏過速症}}
* 小管附睾的微腺瘤
* 组织胺不耐症
* [[前列腺炎|前列腺炎]]
* [[哮喘|哮喘]]
* [[阿兹海默病|阿兹海默病]]
* [[糖尿病|糖尿病]]

== 流行病学 ==
在美国，国家卫生研究院（NIH）的罕见疾病研究办公室认为是一种罕见的疾病。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/GARD/Condition/10809/Postorgasmic_illness_syndrome.aspx |title=Postorgasmic illness syndrome | Disease | Overview |publisher=Office of Rare Diseases Research (ORDR-NCATS) |date= |accessdate=2014-02-23 |archive-date=2012-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120826130946/http://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/GARD/Condition/10809/Postorgasmic_illness_syndrome.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>它也列在国家罕见疾病组织（NORD）的数据库中。<ref>[http://www.rarediseases.org/rare-disease-information/organizations/byID/3136/viewDetail Post Orgasmic Illness Syndrome (P.O.I.S.) Forum] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503062638/http://rarediseases.org/rare-disease-information/organizations/byID/3136/viewDetail |date=2015-05-03 }} National Organization for Rare Disorders</ref>目前该病在中国尚未见报道，绝大多数临床医生从未接触过此类病症，而且此症在全球也是极为少见。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://andrologist.dxyer.cn/879_710/|title=男人也患精液过敏症|accessdate=2015-05-23|work=《健康时报》|publisher=|date=2011年4月16日|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201829/http://andrologist.dxyer.cn/879_710/|archivedate=2016年3月4日}}</ref>

